1
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,460
The pursuers might have someone who knows magic.

2
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:07,460
They can sense us remotely.

3
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:08,230
My lord,

4
00:01:08,260 --> 00:01:09,300
the barking is getting closer.

5
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:11,360
Half an incense stick of time at most.

6
00:01:16,330 --> 00:01:18,530
Baiyun Temple is twenty miles east of the city.

7
00:01:18,530 --> 00:01:20,060
There might be a way to break the pact there.

8
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,360
You must take the official road to get there.

9
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,660
The pursuers will definitely set an ambush.

10
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,360
And it's unknown whether the people in the temple are friends or foes.

11
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:24,660
I...

12
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,860
I remember my father mentioning it.

13
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,200
Daoist Lu of Baiyun Temple

14
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,930
is Uncle Shen's sworn brother.

15
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:30,990
He is trustworthy.

16
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,660
We can't take the official road.

17
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:37,130
Half a mile downstream along the riverbank,

18
00:01:37,130 --> 00:01:38,460
I remember there is a reed marsh.

19
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:39,960
We can hide there until dawn.

20
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:42,820
Then we'll take the mountain path to Baiyun Temple.

21
00:01:45,130 --> 00:01:47,160
You and Miss Gu are connected by the mark.

22
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,259
If she loses control,

23
00:01:48,259 --> 00:01:49,660
you will be affected too.

24
00:01:49,660 --> 00:01:50,860
You must stay awake.

25
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,200
Yeah.

26
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:56,460
Let's go.

27
00:01:56,530 --> 00:01:57,860
Baiyun Temple is currently

28
00:01:57,860 --> 00:01:58,729
our only clue.

29
00:01:59,930 --> 00:02:01,830
If Uncle Lu is really a piece you left behind,

30
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:03,030
please protect us.

31
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,930
The smoke condenses and doesn't dissipate.

32
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:28,300
It contains special medicinal powder.

33
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,400
It's the purifying incense commonly used by Daoists.

34
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,560
This talisman is indeed

35
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,760
an authentic product of Baiyun Temple.

36
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:44,960
I...

37
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,900
I just seemed to hear

38
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,500
a voice in my head saying...

39
00:02:47,530 --> 00:02:48,400
Tell Shen Mo,

40
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,130
The ledger is under the founder's statue.

41
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:51,790
The copper coin is in his arms.

42
00:02:53,130 --> 00:02:54,430
Are you Young Master Shen Mo?

43
00:02:54,430 --> 00:02:56,030
Uncle Lu asked me to wait here.

44
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:56,700
Come in quickly.

45
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:58,360
The pursuers are almost here.

46
00:03:03,130 --> 00:03:03,630
My lord,

47
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,560
beware of a trap.

48
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,400
Thank you, young Daoist.

49
00:03:09,530 --> 00:03:10,930
We'll come in right away.

50
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:12,960
Stay close to me.

51
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,760
Act according to the situation.

52
00:03:24,930 --> 00:03:25,930
Registrar Shen,

53
00:03:25,930 --> 00:03:27,660
I've been waiting for a long time.

54
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:29,560
Lord Qin predicted you would come here.

55
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,829
Qin Muzhi's subordinate.

56
00:03:30,829 --> 00:03:32,300
Your disguise skills are too poor.

57
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:32,900
Young Daoist,

58
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,630
pretending must be hard on you.

59
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,060
Go!

60
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:37,300
Mo'er!

61
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,160
Run!

62
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,160
It's a trap.

63
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,660
They captured all the disciples in the temple

64
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:43,260
and forced me to lure you out.

65
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:45,200
Daoist Lu,

66
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,530
don't forget your disciples.

67
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:48,030
Qin Muzhi colluded with the Third Prince

68
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,460
to seize what brother Shen Qingshan left behind,

69
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:50,460
the account book and the copper coin.

70
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,860
The book holds evidence of them funding evil arrays

71
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:53,230
and trading officials' lives.

72
00:03:53,230 --> 00:03:54,760
The copper coin is one of three tokens.

73
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,829
Combined, they reveal Tianji Pavilion's location.

74
00:03:56,829 --> 00:03:57,230
Mo'er,

75
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:58,890
you must not let them succeed.

76
00:03:59,160 --> 00:03:59,960
Uncle Lu,

77
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:00,900
you talk too much.

78
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:01,230
Shen Mo,

79
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:03,060
hand over your two blood chalcedonies.

80
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:04,400
Tell us what you found in Gu Wenyuan's secret room,

81
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,860
and we will leave Lu Mingyuan a whole corpse.

82
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:06,400
Otherwise,

83
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,760
the 12 Daoists in the temple,

84
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,560
including this child,

85
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,220
will die before you one by one.

86
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:11,660
You laid an ambush here,

87
00:04:11,930 --> 00:04:13,460
fearing I'd meet Daoist Lu

88
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,260
and get clues.

89
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,260
So,

90
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,430
the account book and copper coin

91
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,290
haven't been found by you, right?

92
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:23,030
Did you know

93
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:24,830
the mother contract on Miss Gu

94
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:26,130
might be connected

95
00:04:26,130 --> 00:04:27,160
to one of you?

96
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:29,300
Qin Muzhi masters soul control.

97
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,530
Haven't you death soldiers

98
00:04:30,530 --> 00:04:32,400
been planted with child contracts?

99
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,730
If Miss Gu triggers the mother contract now,

100
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:35,930
all of you

101
00:04:35,930 --> 00:04:37,330
might suffer a backlash.

102
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,430
You protect Miss Gu and Xiaocui.

103
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,300
Rush to the main hall's left corridor.

104
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,360
There is a side door.

105
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,260
I'll save Uncle Lu.

106
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:41,720
My lord.

107
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:00,760
Go!

108
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,330
Go to the secret passage behind the main hall.

109
00:05:02,330 --> 00:05:03,390
I'll hold them off.

110
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,230
Uncle Lu!

111
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:07,330
Brother Qingshan gave me a second life.

112
00:05:07,330 --> 00:05:09,130
Today, I shall repay him.

113
00:05:09,130 --> 00:05:09,730
Mo'er,

114
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:10,330
remember.

115
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:11,530
When three coins unite,

116
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:13,300
the map to Tianji Pavilion will appear.

117
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:16,160
Behind Qin Muzhi is the Imperial Astronomy Bureau.

118
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,300
Go!

119
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,460
Mo'er,

120
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:39,730
when you grow up, be like your father.

121
00:05:39,730 --> 00:05:41,030
Be an upright

122
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:42,560
and discerning official.

123
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:43,820
Brother Lu,

124
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:45,159
if anything happens to me,

125
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,700
I entrust Mo'er to you.

126
00:05:47,130 --> 00:05:48,800
Why say that, Brother Qingshan?

127
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,600
We are brothers,

128
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,760
sharing life and death together.

129
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,960
Brother Qingshan,

130
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,220
I am coming to find you.

131
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:00,900
Shen Mo,

132
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,430
you can't escape.

133
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:05,200
Lord Qin has cast an inescapable net.

134
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,960
Imperial Clan Court.

135
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,100
Tianji Pavilion.

136
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:24,960
Uncle Lu said three coins unite,

137
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,890
the map appears.

138
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,930
My lord,

139
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:29,530
the mark is burning.

140
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,560
We can't leave through the exit.

141
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,360
This secret passage

142
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,960
should have other branches.

143
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,600
Let's go look over there.
